# ntscli-cloud-lib

This repo contains the python interface for the NTS-CLI 2.0 implementation of the Automator over IoT.

[Basic descriptions of NTS-CLI and getting started are here.](https://manuals.netflix.net/view/ntscli-docs/mkdocs/master/)

[API Reference documentation is kept in this repo, but published here](https://manuals.netflix.net/view/ntscli-cloud-lib/mkdocs/master/)
